$DEF_VAR
Local Char     LIGNE(250)
Local Char     NOMVAR(255)
Local Date     DAT
Local Integer  LIBEL
# Usadas SOLO en EXPORT1 y EXPORT2
Local Char     ACTION(20)
Local Char     EXPFIC(GLONABR)
Local Integer  OK
Return

Funprog INTERLOCUTOR_PAIS(COD)
Value Char COD
Local Char PAIS(GLONCRY)
If !clalev([F:AIN])      :  Local File CONTACTCRM      [F:AIN]  : Endif
Read [F:AIN]AIN0=COD
If fstat=0 PAIS=[F:AIN]CRY Else Raz PAIS Endif
End PAIS

